{"tid":940352,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"車仔發聲明譴責反閃族球迷","createTime":"2018-12-14T01:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T01:25:07.000Z","uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ba71fcd05605e7f67a6532e056062a4efa0848ee","tid":940352,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:01:11.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Xm7WKmrItRA9qTfGUjZ%2FazQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=74839156\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】部份車路士球迷在歐霸盃分組賽大叫反閃族的口號，遭會方發表聲明譴責。<br />\n<br />\n車路士球迷大概是全英國其中最不聽話的球迷，上次對曼城的種族辱罵史達寧的風波未平，周四歐霸盃分組賽作客2:2和匈牙利的維迪奧頓，又鬧出球迷高呼反閃族口號的事件，恐怕又難逃歐洲足協的處罰，會方賽後也馬上發表聲明譴責。<br />\n<br />\n聲明寫道：「反閃族以及一切不尊重種族、宗教的行為，都違反球會和大部份車路士球迷的價值觀。我們不容許這樣的球迷存在。我們從班主、董事局、教練、球員，都大聲疾呼反對這樣的做法！我們將嚴懲這樣的球迷。」<br />\n<br />\n車仔確做了該做的事，今年1月還舉行活動，教育球迷要捨棄反閃族的做法，可惜部份球迷依然重犯，實在令球會萬分無奈。"},{"pid":"bb132a5c7ab874f7b43b6b06abc358106875b3d9","tid":940352,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8493b8a62298445e9f4e9abe6b8746cb39d3618a","tid":940352,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:11:23.000Z","msg":"連登族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5128650889443753116aef0538bc8d5bc07159a4","tid":940352,"uid":97,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:12:19.000Z","msg":"油王好似都係猶太人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0da4db8fe4e7866ab7fee63bb7bb4c57cd75002","tid":940352,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:13:22.000Z","msg":"咩係反閃族"},{"pid":"326cdeaae37bda64b192c3490c6a9558cbb46371","tid":940352,"uid":60726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0da4db8fe4e7866ab7fee63bb7bb4c57cd75002","tid":940352,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0